cff-version: 1.2.0
title: IntelCue MCP Server
message: >-
  IntelCue is an AI-first market and competitive intelligence platform that
  delivers live insights into Claude and other AI assistants via the Model
  Context Protocol (MCP).
type: software
authors:
  - name: IntelCue
url: https://www.intelcue.ai
repository-code: https://github.com/intelcue/intelcue-mcp
abstract: >-
  The IntelCue MCP server is a hosted, remote Model Context Protocol server that
  exposes read-only market and competitive intelligence tools — trending topics,
  competitive alerts, keywords and hashtags, and content
  from newsletters, blogs, news, YouTube, websites, Google Ads,
  patents, Certificate Transparency (new subdomains), and more — scoped to the authenticated IntelCue workspace.
keywords:
  - model context protocol
  - mcp
  - competitive intelligence
  - market intelligence
  - ai agents
  - claude
license: MIT
